Todo CLI App

This is a simple command-line Todo application built with Node.js.

## Features
- Add tasks
- List tasks
- Mark tasks as done
- Delete tasks

## Usage
\`\`\`bash
node todo.js add \"Learn Node.js\"
node todo.js list
node todo.js done 1
node todo.js delete 2
\`\`\`

Tasks are stored in a JSON file (tasks.json).
